---
import { GOLF_KITS, CTA_RICHIEDI_PREZZO } from '../../data/golf-kits';
---
<section id="kit" class="bg-cream py-24 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow text-ink/70">i kit</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-display-tight text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-[1] mb-6 max-w-3xl" data-reveal>
      Tre idee di kit, grafica inclusa.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-ink/70 max-w-2xl mb-14" data-reveal>
      Non un catalogo infinito a preventivo: tre composizioni pensate per le esigenze reali di sponsor, circolo e stagione. Scrivete il vostro caso, vi rispondiamo con il prezzo.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {GOLF_KITS.map((kit) => (
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-white border-2 border-ink/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-orange transition" data-reveal>
          {kit.image ? (
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-light">
              <img src={kit.image} alt={kit.name} class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="600" height="450" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          ) : (
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-light flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-ink/30 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide px-4 text-center">Foto in arrivo</span>
            </div>
          )}
          <div class="flex flex-col flex-1 p-8">
            <span class="eyebrow text-orange mb-4">{kit.eyebrow}</span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink mb-3 leading-tight">{kit.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-ink/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">{kit.tagline}</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8 text-sm text-ink/70">
              {kit.includes.map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-orange font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
                  <span set:html={item} />
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <p class="text-xs text-ink/50 mb-6">Grafica inclusa, consegna confermata per la data gara</p>
              <a
                href={`/golf/${kit.slug}`}
                class="btn-orange block text-center bg-orange text-cream py-4 px-6 text-sm font-bold tracking-wide rounded-full hover:bg-ink transition"
                style="text-decoration:none;"
              >
                {CTA_RICHIEDI_PREZZO} →
              </a>
              <a href={`/golf/${kit.slug}`} class="block text-center text-xs text-ink/50 mt-3 hover:text-orange transition">
                Vedi il dettaglio del kit
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
